<h1>HTML Text Formatting</h1>

<p>
<b>HTML</b> is used to create <i>web pages</i>.  
It supports <u>text formatting</u> such as 
<strong>bold</strong>, <em>italic</em>, and 
<mark>highlighted</mark> text.
</p>

<p>
This is <small>small text</small> and this is 
<big>big text</big>.  
Water formula: H<sub>2</sub>O  
Square of 5: 5<sup>2</sup>
</p>

